                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <blockquote>
                            &ldquo;I, and ALL my employees, were able to see progress, which was so nice for my own work - I don&rsquo;t frequently see progress in a short amount of time in my current role.&rdquo;
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <blockquote>
                            &ldquo;It is so fun to be part of such a positive, helpful project that really made an impact on people&rsquo;s lives.&rdquo;
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <blockquote>
                            &ldquo;The HPS Brain Gym program prioritized the coaches as much as the clients.&rdquo;
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <blockquote>
                            &ldquo;Refreshing to work with people who have the energy, interest, time, curiosity, space, and privilege in self-reflection.&rdquo;
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <a class="btn btn-blue btn-oversized" href="/the-science">
        The science behind HPS Brain Gym&trade; {{ macros.icon('chevron-right') }}
    </a>


{% endblock %}